messages.message:
Hey, question from ANZ prospect (ST AI Hub instance): "If we have multiple teams working with AI Hub solutions, can they have different platform versions?"

Presumably these separate teams would operate in their own workspaces? He sees the benefit being that often teams want to update at different cadences/when it is convenient for them. If the version of AI Hub and updates are managed centrally, then teams lose the independence that they get with on-prem distinct environments
